SUMMARY:Vibe Coding a Website (For Non-Technical Users)
DESCRIPTION:All Things AI (Live)\n**You don't need to learn to code. You n
 eed to learn to communicate with AI.**\n\nWhat if you could go from "I hav
 e a business idea" to a live\, professional website in about an hour — w
 ithout writing a single line of code yourself? That's not a hypothetical. 
 That's what we're going to do together.\nVibe Coding is a hands-on worksho
 p where you'll use AI tools to build and deploy a real\, production-ready 
 website. Not a toy. Not a template. A fully custom site with contact forms
 \, newsletter signup\, SEO optimization\, mobile responsiveness\, accessib
 ility compliance\, and security headers — the works. You'll tell the AI 
 what you want\, and a team of 19 specialized AI skills will handle the imp
 lementation.\nI've been in tech since before the web existed — from BBSs
  to open source to cloud to AI — and I haven't been this excited about a
  technology shift since the early internet days. We're at the point where 
 the barrier between "I have an idea" and "here's my website" is basically 
 a conversation. And I want to show you how.\n\n### What You'll Walk Away W
 ith\n\n* A live\, professionally built website deployed on Vercel with a c
 ustom domain\, SSL\, and CDN\n* Hands-on experience using AI agents to han
 dle brand discovery\, design\, content\, forms\, and deployment\n* A repea
 table workflow you can use for future projects — for yourself or your cl
 ients\n* The confidence to build web projects without waiting on (or payin
 g for) a developer\n\n### What We'll Cover\n\n**Core Workshop (\\~1 Hour):
 **\n\n* Introduction to the Vibe Coding methodology — what it is and why
  it works\n* Brand discovery: teaching AI who you are and what you need\n*
  Website generation from your requirements using specialized AI skills\n* 
 Deploying your site live to the internet\n\n**Expanded Deep Dive (Addition
 al Time for Those Who Want More):**\n\n* Branding and AI image generation 
 strategies\n* Content optimization and persuasive copywriting\n* Advanced 
 features: newsletter integration\, contact forms\, analytics\n* Performanc
 e tuning and SEO fundamentals\n* Quality assurance — the full audit batt
 ery\n\n### Before You Arrive: What You'll Need\n\nThis is a hands-on works
 hop. To follow along and build your own site\, please set up these free ac
 counts before the event:\n\n1. **GitHub Account** (free) — [github.com](
 https://github.com) This is where your website code will live. If you don'
 t have one\, sign up — it takes two minutes.\n2. **Vercel Account with v
 0** (free) — [v0.app/ref/VQQW5K](https://v0.app/ref/VQQW5K) Vercel is wh
 ere your site gets deployed. v0 is their AI-powered development tool. Sign
  up through this link and we both earn $5 in credits. When you subscribe\,
  we both earn $20 in credits.\n3. **An AI Platform** — Pick one (or brin
 g all three):\n\n* **Manus** (easiest to use) — [manus.im/invitation/NAG
 Z9RPPM9OYOD](https://manus.im/invitation/NAGZ9RPPM9OYOD?utm_source=invitat
 ion&utm_medium=social&utm_campaign=copy_link)\n* **Claude** (my preferred 
 platform for the code) — [claude.ai](https://claude.ai)\n* **ChatGPT** 
 — [chatgpt.com](https://chatgpt.com)\n\n4. **Your brand idea** — Know 
 what kind of site you want to build. A business\, a portfolio\, a side pro
 ject\, a community page — anything works. Come with a rough idea of who 
 you serve and what you do.\n\n**No coding experience required.** Seriously
 . If you can describe what you want in plain English\, you have everything
  you need.\n\n### Who Is This For?\n\n* Entrepreneurs and small business o
 wners who need a website but don't want to pay $5\,000+ for one\n* Markete
 rs and content creators who want to prototype landing pages fast\n* Consul
 tants and freelancers who want to offer web services without learning to c
 ode\n* Curious professionals who want to see what AI can actually do right
  now — not in some hypothetical future\n* Developers who want to 10x the
 ir speed by letting AI handle the boilerplate\n\n### The Tech (For the Cur
 ious)\n\nYour site will be built with standard HTML5\, CSS3\, and JavaScri
 pt — no proprietary lock-in\, no walled gardens. The code is portable\, 
 readable\, and yours to keep. It deploys on Vercel with automatic CDN\, SS
 L\, and global edge delivery. The AI handles everything from brand voice t
 o WCAG accessibility compliance to Core Web Vitals optimization.\nCourse m
 aterials are open source: [github.com/mrhinkle/VibeCoding-a-Website](https
 ://github.com/mrhinkle/VibeCoding-a-Website)
